{"tid":553333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「泰」爽了! 男娶雙胞胎 婚後三人行...","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T15:29:59.000Z","uid":25345,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"90d53e678cd141c7f4cde3e076803f22dadbe847","tid":553333,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201503/201503301598568_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201503%2F201503301598568_l.jpg&h=ec602fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要找到終身伴侶，實在不容易，但泰國夜功府(Samut Songkram)的一名杜姓男子(Winchao Tao)，一次就娶走一對雙胞胎姐妹，羨煞不少光棍族。<br />\n<br />\n據《backchina》報導，這名享盡齊人之福的男子，與雙胞胎「妻子們」是青梅竹馬，從小到大玩在一起，形影不離，連交往都是「三人行」。杜男到了適婚年齡想成家，但他無法捨棄雙胞胎姐妹中的任何一位，最後提起勇起，向兩姊妹求婚，而兩姊妹竟也爽快的一口答應。<br />\n<br />\n不過一次娶兩個，聘禮也要付兩倍，兩姊妹各要求122克黃金及1.9萬港幣(約10萬台幣)當嫁妝。據了解，三位新人新婚夜也分成兩天，兩位妻子進了夫家後，各獲一間房，婚後她們先各陪丈夫一晚，第三晚便開始三人同睡。事件曝光後，有網友更酸杜男：「開始爽死，往後就等死囉」。"},{"pid":"b533883e623e0e51ad4a26fd9b8a8a9b92e4d60c","tid":553333,"uid":164930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d21951f48bf0e01331d5b6bca48ebfdbd217da","tid":553333,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"泰國可以咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4d795d9e83016d49f8baa6dd0c350b13cc7a02","tid":553333,"uid":1367,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"屌同一條女托咩"},{"pid":"6ce2f8cd78c9b2c52a7bf5887426e32b2963e2c6","tid":553333,"uid":19126,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"三個人，有三碌棍......"},{"pid":"e54c68438f31cd8a62767e96cc1d81343704c085","tid":553333,"uid":32841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ce2f8cd78c9b2c52a7bf5887426e32b2963e2c6","tid":553333,"uid":19126,"li